MergeObjects

MergeObjects.Rd

This function merges niche-DE objects

Usage

MergeObjects(objects)

Arguments

objects

A list of niche-DE objects

Value

A niche-DE object with each niche-DE object that concatenates each niche-DE object used in the input list. Coordinates are scaled to ensure that kernel bandwidths are consistent across datasets
